  "detailed_description": "<ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Lightweight but powerful. Optimized for Steam Workshop and customizable.<br></li><li>Relaxing or hardcore gaming. Control the difficulty by number of pieces and time, obstacle.<br></li><li>Basically works in random mode. Also you can play the puzzles you want in the gallery.<br></li><li>Easily customize the puzzle images and themes from made with community or yourself.<br></li><li>Steam Achievements, Workshop. Cross-platform auto-cloud sync with Steam Cloud.<br></li><li>Full Controller support with Steam Input.</li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >1st theme: TOGETHER</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1045400/extras/891f9ffc5c78d28e94107b88dd9a63af.avif?t=1699229116\" width=610 height=140 /></span><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>The first theme with the release is <strong>\"TOGETHER\"</strong>.<br></li><li>You can play 100 retouched images with jigsaw puzzle.</li></ul>",
